data.description: You will fall in love as soon as you walk into this gorgeous Victorian Home located just minutes to Downtown Hampton and easy access to the interstate.  Updated kitchen with new stainless appliances and granite countertops, beautiful hardwood flooring throughout, wood burning fireplace in large family room with built in bookcases.  Downstairs you have a nice size office or it could be a 4th bedroom.  Full bath down and full bath up.  Large laundry room and the pull down attic is huge.  Detached 400 square foot workshop and a large deck great for those summer cookouts.
